---
// ProcessJourney — always-visible editorial section that explains the process after the funnel area.
// Keeps the narrative stable on the page instead of treating it like a stateful funnel step.
---

<section
  class="process-journey surface-sage-wash"
  aria-labelledby="process-journey-heading"
>
  <div class="process-shell">
    <header class="process-header">
      <p class="process-kicker">Metodo VIA(R)</p>
      <div class="process-header-grid">
        <div class="process-intro">
          <h2 id="process-journey-heading" class="process-heading" tabindex="-1">
            Camino de Evolución Consciente
          </h2>
          <p class="process-subheading">
            Comprender lo vivido para elegir con mas claridad lo que queres construir ahora.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="process-note" aria-label="Enfoque del proceso">
          No buscamos cambiar quien sos; ampliamos la manera en que comprendes tu experiencia para tomar decisiones con mas consciencia y libertad.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="process-body">
      <section class="process-section process-section-topics" aria-labelledby="process-topics-heading">
        <div class="process-section-header">
          <h3 id="process-topics-heading">Temas que suelen aparecer</h3>
          <p>
            Cada recorrido es singular, pero estos son algunos de los focos que suelen necesitar mas comprension, orden y direccion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-topic-clusters" aria-label="Temas del proceso">
          <article class="process-cluster">
            <h4>Vinculos</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Relaciones de pareja</li>
              <li>Vinculos familiares</li>
              <li>Autoestima</li>
              <li>Pertenencia y vinculos</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="process-cluster">
            <h4>Patrones y recursos internos</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Patrones repetitivos</li>
              <li>Miedos e inseguridades</li>
              <li>Gestion emocional</li>
              <li>Identidad</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="process-cluster">
            <h4>Direccion</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Proposito de vida</li>
              <li>Dinero y prosperidad</li>
              <li>Trabajo y vocacion</li>
              <li>Toma de decisiones</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <aside class="process-rail" aria-label="Recursos y objetivo del proceso">
        <section class="process-rail-block process-section-outcome" aria-labelledby="process-outcome-heading">
          <h3 id="process-outcome-heading">Objetivo del proceso</h3>
          <p>
            Favorecer una comprension mas profunda de vos, identificar recursos internos y transformar lo que hoy vivis en decisiones con mas coherencia y libertad.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="process-rail-block process-section-tools" aria-labelledby="process-tools-heading">
          <h3 id="process-tools-heading">Recursos que pueden integrarse</h3>
          <p>
            Segun cada caso, el profesional puede combinar herramientas de acompanamiento para sostener un proceso personalizado.
          </p>

          <ul class="process-tools-list">
            <li>Coaching</li>
            <li>Programacion Neurolinguistica</li>
            <li>Constelaciones Familiares</li>
            <li>Biodescodificacion</li>
            <li>Memoria Celular</li>
            <li>Hipnosis</li>
            <li>Reiki</li>
            <li>Tameana</li>
            <li>Mindfulness</li>
            <li>Meditacion</li>
            <li>Visualizaciones guiadas</li>
            <li>Gestion emocional</li>
            <li>Reencuadre de creencias</li>
            <li>Tecnicas de autoconocimiento</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <p class="process-legal">
          Aviso profesional: esta es una propuesta orientada al desarrollo personal. No constituye atencion medica, psicologica ni psiquiatrica y no reemplaza tratamientos de salud.
        </p>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process-journey {
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem) 1.25rem clamp(2.75rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .process-shell {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }

  .process-header {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(211, 202, 189, 0.7);
  }

  .process-header-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 44rem) minmax(16rem, 22rem);
    gap: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .process-intro {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    max-width: 44rem;
  }

  .process-kicker {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--via-rust, #b46430);
  }

  .process-heading {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 12ch;
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4.4vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: var(--via-night-blue);
    text-wrap: balance;
    outline: none;
  }

  .process-subheading {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 34ch;
    font-family: var(--ff-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.34rem);
    line-height: 1.28;
    color: rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.78);
  }

  .process-lead {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 52ch;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.68;
    color: var(--via-gray-600);
  }

  .process-note {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 22rem;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(180, 100, 48, 0.28);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.64;
    color: rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.78);
  }

  .process-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.45fr) minmax(17rem, 0.78fr);
    gap: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .process-section {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }

  .process-section-topics {
    padding-right: clamp(0rem, 1vw, 0.75rem);
  }

  .process-section-header {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    max-width: 42ch;
  }

  .process-section-header h3,
  .process-rail h3 {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--via-night-blue);
  }

  .process-section-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.08rem;
  }

  .process-section-header p,
  .process-rail-block p,
  .process-section-outcome p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.94rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--via-gray-600);
  }

  .process-topic-clusters {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .process-cluster:last-child {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    max-width: 24rem;
  }

  .process-cluster {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    padding-top: 0.85rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(211, 202, 189, 0.72);
  }

  .process-cluster h4 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.92);
  }

  .process-cluster ul,
  .process-tools-list {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.55rem;
  }

  .process-cluster li,
  .process-tools-list li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    align-items: start;
    font-size: 0.94rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--via-night-blue);
  }

  .process-cluster li::before,
  .process-tools-list li::before {
    content: '';
    width: 0.4rem;
    height: 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(180, 100, 48, 0.7);
  }

  .process-rail {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(211, 202, 189, 0.7);
  }

  .process-rail-block {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-top: 0.95rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(211, 202, 189, 0.72);
  }

  .process-rail h3 {
    font-size: 0.96rem;
  }

  .process-tools-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0.42rem;
  }

  .process-tools-list li {
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    color: rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.82);
  }

  .process-section-outcome {
    padding-top: 0;
    border-top: 0;
  }

  .process-legal {
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: 0.9rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(211, 202, 189, 0.6);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.52;
    color: rgba(26, 39, 68, 0.58);
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .process-header-grid,
    .process-body,
    .process-topic-clusters {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .process-heading {
      max-width: 16ch;
    }

    .process-note {
      padding-left: 0;
      border-left: 0;
      padding-top: 0.9rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(180, 100, 48, 0.22);
    }

    .process-rail {
      padding-left: 0;
      border-left: 0;
      padding-top: 1rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(211, 202, 189, 0.7);
    }

    .process-tools-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .process-journey {
      padding: 2rem 1rem 2.4rem;
    }

    .process-shell {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .process-heading {
      max-width: none;
      font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 9vw, 2.3rem);
      line-height: 1.04;
    }

    .process-lead,
    .process-subheading,
    .process-section-header p,
    .process-section-outcome p,
    .process-note,
    .process-legal {
      font-size: 0.93rem;
    }

    .process-subheading {
      max-width: none;
      line-height: 1.35;
    }

    .process-topic-clusters {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .process-cluster,
    .process-rail-block {
      padding-top: 0.85rem;
    }

    .process-tools-list {
      gap: 0.35rem;
    }
  }
</style>
